original_title: UFC on ESPN 10: Eye vs. Calvillo
overview: UFC on ESPN 10: Eye vs. Calvillo was a mixed martial arts event produced by the Ultimate Fighting Championship that took place on June 13, 2020 at the UFC Apex facility in Enterprise, Nevada, part of the Las Vegas Metropolitan Area, United States. The women's flyweight bout between former UFC Women's Flyweight Championship challenger Jessica Eye and Cynthia Calvillo served as the new event headliner.
title: UFC on ESPN 10: Eye vs. Calvillo
